# Planner-First

For any multi-step implementation request, delegate to the planner agent first. The planner orchestrates: worker -> git.

Do not bypass the planner for multi-file work.

Exempt: single-file edits, read-only questions.

> **STOP.** Before any Write, StrReplace, or Task call: classify as Trivial or not.
> If not Trivial, your first call MUST be Task(subagent_type="jg-planner").
